match.name: .22LR Team Match 2025
match.about:
Nothing quite like it! Let's do it again!

Trophies Awarded to the Top 5 teams.

$60 per shooter, lunch provided.

FAQ:
Q: Are there Divisions?
A: No. Everyone will be shooting open. Welcome to the Thunderdome.

Q: Can we see the course of fire ahead of time or have an idea of what to expect?
A: No.

Q: Are Semi-autos allowed?
A: No. We built stages and expectations around bolt guns only.

Q: What is the format?
A: The match will be ran like a typical monthly or X match (stages, squads, etc). The main difference is that both team members will be tackling a stage simultaneously. This may include team members shooting at the same time, taking turns shooting, etc.

Q: How physical will it be?
A: About the same physical expectations of a monthly or X match. One stage will have some sprinting/running (15 yards distance multiple times for both team mates). 

Q: How many rounds will we need?
A; A bare minimum of 120, but bring more as one stage is unlimited. Just bring a lot.

Q: How many stages will there be?
A: 10.

Q: Are there gear restrictions?
A: Yes, 1 bag and bipod. At least 2 magazines required.

Q: Do we pick partners or are we assigned partners?
A: You pick your partner. We will not be assigning any partners. Choose wisely.

Q: Will there be morning zero?
A: Yes. Zero starts at 7:30am sharp. It will be in a designated area. Absolutely NO shooting of any steel placed out for the match. Stage walkthroughs after zero and safety brief.

Jim & David.
